{"tid":2006644,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美俄領袖通電話　特朗普籲將中國納入新一輪限武談判","createTime":"2020-05-08T02:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T03:49:42.000Z","uid":152476,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c5be6da5be97f95550b0332b8953ee130d3cc9a7","tid":2006644,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 🇺🇸 🇷🇺 <br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普和俄羅斯總統普京通電話。特朗普呼籲中國參與新一輪限制軍備的談判。<br />\n<br />\n白宮發表聲明說，特朗普重申，美國致力實行有效的軍備限制，不止俄羅斯，中國亦應該參與，並期待今後能夠展開討論，以避免高昂的軍備競賽。<br />\n<br />\n兩國領袖通話期間亦談及新型冠狀病毒疫情，特朗普重申，美國除了致力照顧國內民眾，亦準備向包括俄羅斯在內的國家，提供所需援助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524930-20200508.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524930-20200508.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0KQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=6d14753d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524930-20200508.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=95300de1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524930-20200508.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c50609bf43f6ae4b247c1db7b1b7ce0db170a443","tid":2006644,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:39:46.000Z","msg":"睇來侵侵始終係最叻燃支共既人<br />\n把口舔雜總但行動招招見血"},{"pid":"ec8886094ee6cdd9b00d90798340e4d038a7c6dd","tid":2006644,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58377af2b15f6185d9932d924d6aedc7420b9965","tid":2006644,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.g